78
00:05:17,446 --> 00:05:18,906
Legenda:
AnaLaura

79
00:05:18,907 --> 00:05:20,283
Legenda:
kDragon

80
00:05:20,284 --> 00:05:21,744
Legenda:
Hugo

81
00:05:21,745 --> 00:05:23,205
Legenda:
VUno

82
00:05:23,206 --> 00:05:24,666
Legenda:
Chip

